        "start": "00:10.000",
        "end": "00:11.800",
        "original": "うん。",
        "english": "Yeah.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:12.600",
        "end": "00:13.900",
        "original": "よかった、よかった。",
        "english": "It was so good, so good.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:14.300",
        "end": "00:16.300",
        "original": "テンション上がるわー、これ。",
        "english": "This is really getting me pumped up.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:20.100",
        "end": "00:24.000",
        "original": "さ、さあ次は、いよいよカノンさんに歌っていただきます！",
        "english": "N-Now then, up next, Kanon-san will finally be performing for us!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:35.300",
        "end": "00:36.400",
        "original": "君、",
        "english": "Are you...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:36.700",
        "end": "00:37.900",
        "original": "大丈夫？",
        "english": "...okay?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:41.000",
        "end": "00:41.800",
        "original": "あ、なに？",
        "english": "Wait, what?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:41.900",
        "end": "00:42.500",
        "original": "なにこれ！",
        "english": "What's this?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:42.600",
        "end": "00:43.100",
        "original": "なになに！",
        "english": "What's going on?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:43.200",
        "end": "00:44.200",
        "original": "なんなのなの？",
        "english": "What is it, nano?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:56.000",
        "end": "00:56.600",
        "original": "え？",
        "english": "Huh?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:57.300",
        "end": "00:58.700",
        "original": "えぇー！？",
        "english": "Whaaaaat?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "00:59.300",
        "end": "01:00.000",
        "original": "あわ...",
        "english": "Oh...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:00.100",
        "end": "01:01.800",
        "original": "あわって...",
        "english": "Oh my...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:02.800",
        "end": "01:04.000",
        "original": "まさか！",
        "english": "No way!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:07.500",
        "end": "01:08.300",
        "original": "うわぁ！",
        "english": "Whoa!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:10.700",
        "end": "01:12.200",
        "original": "取れないんだけど！",
        "english": "I can't get it off!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:12.300",
        "end": "01:14.000",
        "original": "なにこれ！",
        "english": "What is this thing?!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:14.600",
        "end": "01:15.500",
        "original": "ちょちょちょちょちょ！",
        "english": "Whoa whoa whoa whoa!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:16.400",
        "end": "01:18.000",
        "original": "なになに？どういうこと？",
        "english": "What? What's happening?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:18.600",
        "end": "01:19.400",
        "original": "コラプサーだ！",
        "english": "It's a Corrupsa!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:19.800",
        "end": "01:21.800",
        "original": "ですよね、どう考えてもね！",
        "english": "Of course it is, no matter how you look at it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:22.300",
        "end": "01:24.000",
        "original": "コラプサー。やっぱり。",
        "english": "A Corrupsa. Just as I thought.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:33.700",
        "end": "01:35.300",
        "original": "痛い痛い痛い！",
        "english": "Ow ow ow ow!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:37.600",
        "end": "01:38.800",
        "original": "わりゃ！",
        "english": "Take that!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:39.400",
        "end": "01:40.800",
        "original": "怖い怖い怖い！",
        "english": "Scary, scary, scary!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:41.300",
        "end": "01:43.200",
        "original": "えーと、こういう時は...",
        "english": "U-Um, in times like these...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:45.000",
        "end": "01:47.000",
        "original": "ト、トリック・オア・トリート！",
        "english": "T-Trick or Treat!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:47.400",
        "end": "01:49.000",
        "original": "何もかも違うだろ！",
        "english": "That's wrong in every possible way!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "01:59.000",
        "end": "02:01.500",
        "original": "顔が、顔が変になってるよ！",
        "english": "Her face... her face is turning weird!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:02.500",
        "end": "02:03.500",
        "original": "フブちゃん！",
        "english": "Fubu-chan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:06.500",
        "end": "02:07.500",
        "original": "フブちゃん！",
        "english": "Fubu-chan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:07.600",
        "end": "02:09.500",
        "original": "出てる出てる！楽しいの素が出たな！",
        "english": "It's coming out! Her essence of fun is coming out!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:09.600",
        "end": "02:11.000",
        "original": "よいしょ！",
        "english": "Heave-ho!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:17.300",
        "end": "02:20.500",
        "original": "でも、コラプサーが出てくるってことは...",
        "english": "Ugh... But if the Corrupsas are appearing...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:21.300",
        "end": "02:24.600",
        "original": "夢落ちしてる人がいるんだ、多分。",
        "english": "Someone must be suffering a Dream Fall, probably.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:29.000",
        "end": "02:29.800",
        "original": "ミオ先輩！",
        "english": "Mio-senpai!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:30.800",
        "end": "02:31.700",
        "original": "ミオちゃん！",
        "english": "Mio-chan!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:34.600",
        "end": "02:36.400",
        "original": "ご、ごめん。うち、うち...",
        "english": "I-I'm sorry. I... I...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:37.000",
        "end": "02:39.400",
        "original": "本当は、本当は...",
        "english": "Actually, actually...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:40.600",
        "end": "02:43.400",
        "original": "ハロウィンのカボチャが怖くてだめなのー！",
        "english": "I'm just so terrified of Halloween pumpkins that I can't do anything!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:47.900",
        "end": "02:53.000",
        "original": "ちっちゃい頃、パパがハロウィンであれ被って帰ってきて...",
        "english": "When I was little, my dad came home for Halloween wearing one of those...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:53.600",
        "end": "02:55.300",
        "original": "ただいまー",
        "english": "I'm home!",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:54.400",
        "end": "02:58.200",
        "original": "うち、パパがカボチャに食べられちゃったんだって思っちゃって。",
        "english": "And I thought a pumpkin had eaten my daddy.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:58.300",
        "end": "03:00.000",
        "original": "ハッピーハロウィーン！！",
        "english": "Happy Halloween!!",
        "alignment_source": "visual_inference",
        "type": "on_screen_text"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:00.000",
        "end": "03:02.500",
        "original": "それから、",
        "english": "Ever since then,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:03.700",
        "end": "03:05.500",
        "original": "どうしても、",
        "english": "no matter what,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:06.900",
        "end": "03:10.500",
        "original": "ハロウィンのカボチャだけは、",
        "english": "Halloween pumpkins are the one thing",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:10.600",
        "end": "03:14.000",
        "original": "無理なのー！",
        "english": "I just can't handle!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:38.600",
        "end": "03:39.600",
        "original": "チェンジ！",
        "english": "Change!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:41.200",
        "end": "03:42.500",
        "original": "ガーディアン・アーム！",
        "english": "Guardian Arm!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:43.000",
        "end": "03:44.200",
        "original": "巫女神の輪（みこがみのろった）！",
        "english": "Mikogami no Rotta!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:44.800",
