        "original": "みんな...",
        "english": "Everyone...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:02.000",
        "end": "04:04.500",
        "original": "魔法、みんなに見せちゃうけど、いいよね？",
        "english": "We're going to show everyone our magic, okay?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:06.200",
        "end": "04:08.500",
        "original": "うん、そんなこと言ってらんないし。",
        "english": "Yeah, we don't have time to worry about that now.",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:09.500",
        "end": "04:12.600",
        "original": "だよね！夢落ちした人を助ける。それが...",
        "english": "Right! Helping people who suffer a Dream Fall. That is...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:13.200",
        "end": "04:15.800",
        "original": "魔法少女、ホロウィッチ！",
